#1

ok guys I need some help with an article I am writing

I want to pay respect to those we have list in 2016

2016 has been a year in which we have lost so many legends.. so I wanted to pay respect to the Eurovision legends we ahve lost in the last 12 months.

up to now off teh top of my head I can think of:

Terry Wogan (UK commontator & 1998 host)

Esma (Macedonia 2013)

Roger Cicero (Germany 2007)

Corry Brokken (Netherlands 1957)

Sverre Kjelsberg (Norway 1980)

René Angélil (Celine Dion's husband)

If I have missed anybody please tell me

Jānis Vaišļa from Pirates of the Sea ( 2008) died on 9 January 2016.

Lola Novaković ( 1962) died on 3 April 2016.

Denis Čabrić from Regina ( 2009) died on 17 August 2016.

Patricia Fernández from Trigo Limpio ( 1980) died on 27 September 2016.
